eZ GPG extension v0.4.5 README

What is the eZ GPG extension?
================================

eZ GPG is a true eZ publish extension
that provides simple, transparent, secure 
encryption and decryption to eZ publish
using the GNU Privacy Guard, GPG.


eZ GPG version
=======================

The current version of eZ GPG is 0.4.5.
Last Updated: January 29, 2007

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.4.5


