Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using eZ GPG extension:

o  eZ publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ publish version 3.7 or higher.

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 4.4.x or higher.

o  eZ publish must be able to run external command 'gpg'


Installation
============

Details on installing eZ GPG located in the file doc/INSTALL.


Usage
============

Simply install and activate the extension.

Then use the provided template operators in your templates, modules or extensions.


